query: [{'$match': {'institution.city_name': re.compile('New York(?i)', re.IGNORECASE)}}, {'$group': {'_id': {'instName': '$institution.name', 'instZip': '$institution.zipcode'}, 'quantity': {'$sum': 1}}}, {'$sort': {'quantity': -1}}, {'$project': {'Insitution name': '$_id.instName', 'Insitution zip': '$_id.instZip', 'Awards received': '$quantity', '_id': 0}}]
